      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve got to see this absolute beauty. It has been pampered since day one and honestly looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in incredible shape, super clean inside and out, and drives like a dream. I\u2019m really sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to be so happy with it. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
