      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo is a superlative example of A80-generation engineering. It features the legendary 2JZ-GTE twin-sequential turbocharged inline-six, delivering seamless power through the coveted Getrag V160 6-speed manual gearbox. Mechanically pristine, the vehicle retains its factory-spec double-wishbone suspension and Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise lateral grip and power delivery. Every VIN tag is present, and the chassis remains free of any structural modifications or oxidation. With a leak-down test showing optimal cylinder health and a flawlessly functioning cooling system, this specimen offers a rare opportunity to own a preserved benchmark of Japanese performance history.",
